script.name: plugin.sse.consistency.check
script.description: SSE checks if any objects have been removed or destroyed

line.var: 'Removed %s from extension ships because it does not exist'

line.comment: *write to player logbook: printf: fmt='Removed %s from extension ships list, because it does not exist', $ship, null, null, null, null
*write to player logbook: printf: fmt='sorting ships', $ship, null, null, null, null
*write to player logbook: printf: fmt='ship.wares at index %s was null, removing', $index, null, null, null, null
*write to player logbook: printf: fmt='Station does not trade with %s, removing', $ware.name, null, null, null, null

line.text: write to player logbook: printf: fmt=
write to player logbook: printf: fmt=
write to player logbook: printf: fmt=
write to player logbook: printf: fmt=
write to player logbook: printf: fmt=

line.var: 'Removing %s from preferred ships of %s. It is not an extension ship.'

line.comment: *write to player logbook: printf: fmt='Removing Ship %s from preferred ships of %s. It is not an extension ship.', $ship, $ware.name, null, null, null
*write to player logbook: printf: fmt='sorting preferred ships of %s', $ware.name, null, null, null, null
